race.comment: STAR VALOUR (9) returned with a bang off a long break at Lock, then backed it up with a strong chasing effort here last time. Peaking now and looks tough to hold out. LAVA LAD (2) has hit form and is open to further improvement fourth-up over his pet trip. Gets weight relief with the 3kg claimer and is going too well to ignore. OUR DIVINYL (11) faces a sticky draw but has peaks that measure right up. With even luck he'll be fighting out the finish. PRESCIENT (4) showed sharp tactical speed here two weeks ago, only to be nabbed late by LAVA LAD. Sure to have come on from that and will give backers another bold sight.
